Version 1.5.1, 2015-11-23
-------------------------

* Typo fixes in documentation.

* Style fixes in module code and unit tests.


Version 1.5, 2015-03-17
-----------------------

* Official Python 3 support, requires Python 3.3 or later.

* Added HTML5 color algorithm support.

* Expanded documentation.


Version 1.4, 2012-02-10
-----------------------

* Prep work for Python 3 support.

* Packaging fixes.

* 100% test coverage.

* Bugfix: added normalization of integer and percentage rgb()
  triplets, per CSS clipping rules.


Version 1.3.1, 2009-10-24
-------------------------

* Continued documentation expansion.

* Documentation now maintained using Sphinx.


Version 1.3, 2009-05-08
-----------------------

* Major expansion of documentation.


Version 1.2, 2009-03-01
-----------------------

* Corrected a packaging error.


Version 1.1, 2008-12-19
-----------------------

* Minor documentation update.


Version 1.0, 2008-10-28
-----------------------

* Initial stable release.